Then `f ≫ w = f ≫ (g ≫ z) = (f ≫ g) ≫ z = id X ≫ z = z`.
So this works.

For the reverse direction (`←`):
Assume `∀ c : α, Function.Surjective (fun g => f ≫ g)`.
